name: Future Art Access All Art Pass (Golden Key Edition)

metadata.description:
Access All Art Pass ‘Golden Key Edition’

Access All Art Golden Key Edition Holders will receive

1 x Access All Art NFT

1 x Golden Key NFT

1 x Physical Metallic Golden Pass 300 editions only

Golden key unlocks the golden door at the Future Art NFT Mint Shop and Future Art events.

Gold key holders will be able to mint exclusive limited edition artwork.

Gold pass holders will have access to the gold room at all IRL events.

[https://futureart.io](https://futureart.io/)
metadata.name: Access All Art Pass 'Golden Key Edition'
